Text: TCPL Tolls Application Cc Gentlemen For your perusal and comments is a memo outlining the issues raised by the National Energy Board with respect to TransCanada PipeLines Ltds and Tolls application and their relevance to Enron I would be pleased to schedule a time to meet with you to discuss the implications to Enron Alternatively you could call me at or email your comments Thanks Fino Tiberi Manager Government Affairs Enron Energy Services Canada Co Ltd
